data.description: UNDERPRICED! This stunning home feels brand new and is just about ONE year old. It boasts a spacious layout with a desirable open floorplan, bright with natural light, and is nestled inside this beautiful neighborhood on an interior lot. This home has been meticulously maintained. The kitchen is a chef's dream, complete with gas stove, stainless steel appliances, granite countertops, beautiful LARGE island, designer tile backsplash, and a spacious pantry. Kitchen is open to sun-lit breakfast area and living room – wonderful for family gatherings. The gorgeous wood-like floors are throughout all main areas. Outside, the property is equally impressive. The large backyard is perfect for get togethers, relaxing and outdoor entertaining! The covered patio provides shade on sunny days and there's plenty of space for kids and pets to play! Book your viewing today and start your journey towards your dream home!
